      <title>据报道，舒默和杰弗里斯曾警告拜登不要参选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/schumer-jeffries-reportedly-warned-biden-against-his-candidacy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据多篇新闻报道，参议院多数党领袖查克·舒默和众议院少数党领袖哈基姆·杰弗里斯警告总统乔·拜登，他继续参选将危及民主党在 11 月大选中的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/schumer-jeffries-reportedly-warned-biden-against-his-candidacy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 00:44:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
