    <item>
      <title>英国被要求逆转苏纳克的绿色回滚政策以实现净零排放目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/uk-told-to-reverse-sunak-s-green-rollback-to-meet-net-zero-goal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家气候监督机构表示，新工党政府必须“紧急”扭转其保守党前任对绿色能源计划的倒退，以实现英国的净零目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/uk-told-to-reverse-sunak-s-green-rollback-to-meet-net-zero-goal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>非政府组织称前往巴黎的俄罗斯运动员违反了国际奥委会的规定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/russian-athletes-headed-to-paris-break-ioc-rules-and-sponsors-must-act-says-ngo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人权组织称，获得巴黎奥运会参赛资格的俄罗斯和白俄罗斯运动员中，超过一半与军方或国家安全机构有联系，或支持乌克兰战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/russian-athletes-headed-to-paris-break-ioc-rules-and-sponsors-must-act-says-ngo</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚今年将决定新加坡高铁项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/malaysia-to-decide-on-singapore-high-speed-rail-link-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚将在未来几个月决定是否继续建设耗资数十亿美元的吉隆坡和新加坡之间的高速铁路，因为总理安瓦尔·易卜拉欣领导的政府正在权衡越来越少的私人财团提出的提案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/malaysia-to-decide-on-singapore-high-speed-rail-link-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
